      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six. This high-revving power unit delivers linear throttle response through its six individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Notable maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity matches its performance. The chassis remains tight with refreshed bushings and a factory limited-slip differential. While showing signs of honest use consistent with its age, the car maintains excellent compression and a smooth power band through the 8,000 RPM redline. A driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
